OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778350336
OL,3,CNissan to merge UK production lines
OL,4,Cand cut European workforce
OL,6,FCarmaker Nissan has announced plans to
OL,7,Fclose a production line at its
OL,8,FSunderland factory and cut 900 jobs in
OL,9,FEurope as part of fresh restructuring
OL,10,Fefforts.
OL,12,FThe Japanese manufacturer said it will
OL,13,Fbe combining production from two lines
OL,14,Fto one at the Sunderland site, but
OL,15,Fthat will not lead to any job cuts.
OL,17,FHowever, it has also begun talks with
OL,18,FEuropean staff over changes that
OL,19,Finclude the partial closure of its
OL,20,FBarcelona warehouse, and moving to an
OL,21,Fimporter model for its Nordic markets.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
