PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778350336
OL,3,CNissan to merge UK production lines
OL,4,Cand cut European workforce
OL,6,FThis is set to result in some 900 job
OL,7,Flosses in Europe, amounting to about
OL,8,F10% of its workforce in the continent,
OL,9,Faccording to reports.
OL,11,FNissan did not specify which roles
OL,12,Fwould be impacted and at which
OL,13,Flocations within Europe.
OL,15,FIt employed around 6,000 people at its
OL,16,FSunderland factory as of last year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
