PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778350336
OL,3,CNissan to merge UK production lines
OL,4,Cand cut European workforce
OL,6,FThe latest restructuring efforts come
OL,7,Fafter Nissan announced a major
OL,8,Foverhaul last year with the closure of
OL,9,Fseven factories and targeting some
OL,10,F20,000 job cuts globally.
OL,12,FA spokeswoman for Nissan said: "Under
OL,13,Fthe Re:Nissan recovery plan, we have
OL,14,Fbeen taking decisive actions to
OL,15,Fenhance performance and create a
OL,16,Fleaner, more resilient business that
OL,17,Fadapts quickly to market changes.
OL,26,@tD@`OU
