PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778350336
OL,3,CNissan to merge UK production lines
OL,4,Cand cut European workforce
OL,6,F"As part of this approach, today we
OL,7,Fhave opened discussions with our
OL,8,FEuropean employees with a view to
OL,9,Fsimplifying our structures, reducing
OL,10,Fcomplexity, and ensuring we operate in
OL,11,Fa sustainable and profitable way.
OL,13,F"This includes discussions on
OL,14,Fproposals for the partial closure of
OL,15,Four Barcelona warehouse and to move to
OL,16,Fan importer model for our Nordic
OL,17,Fmarkets.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
