PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778350336
OL,3,CNissan to merge UK production lines
OL,4,Cand cut European workforce
OL,6,F"We have also announced that we will
OL,7,Fconsolidate production from two lines
OL,8,Fto one at our Sunderland plant as we
OL,9,Fassess future opportunities to secure
OL,10,Ffull plant utilisation."
OL,12,FThe Re:Nissan plan was launched in a
OL,13,Fbid to boost the company's performance
OL,14,Fand profits and involves significant
OL,15,Fcost-cutting.
OL,17,FThe company has come under pressure
OL,18,Ffrom slower sales and the impact of
OL,19,Ftariff costs under US President Donald
OL,20,FTrump's trade policies.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]
